    CoinMarketPlus is an emerging marketplace for Blockchain based project, token sales,and initial coin launching. In short frame of time, we have received overwhelming appreciation for our work. With a seasoned and neat-handed team of experts, we are heading toward to achieve a great success. We have team of dedicated and passionate professionals who have sound knowledge of cryptocurrency and cutting-edge technologies like Blockchain.   Crypto market is a lucrative industry and with the passage of time, we are observing plenty of innovation and new marketing strategies. So to discover new strategy, we are looking for some technology enthusiast folks who have interest in crypto industry and decent technical skill. To encourage the technical people, we are announcing the scholarship program for bright and talented brain from all over the globe.  
    About the Scholarship:
    The scholarship is for all those, who want to make a successful career in information technology. The amount of the scholarship is $ 2000.  
    Eligibility for the Scholarship:
    • A Graduate, Under Graduate and Post Graduate students from any educational institute from all over the globe, is eligible for the Scholarship.
    • Must apply to the contest via email and provide your name, address, and the name of the institution you are attending or plan to attend.
    • There is no fee to avail the Scholarship.
    • Minimum GPA must be 3.0
    • Employees at CoinMarketPlus and their family members are not eligible/participate for the scholarship.
    • Last date of receiving application is 12th November, 2018.
    Application Process:

    Applicants have to give an excellent article of around 1500 words on any one of the following topics:

    The Future of Blockchain technology

    Or

    Cryptocurrency, Its Impact on Economy

    Or

    Top Five Cryptocurrencies of 2018, Except Bitcoin

    You have to send your presentation at [email protected]

     
    How we will review the application:
    • All articles will be reviewed by the CoinMarketPlus Scholarship Committee composed of staff members.
    • The article should be unique and high-quality.
    • We will Announce the winner on 30th November, 2018 and will provide the Scholarship amount.
